TITLE: Episode 120 - The Birth of Love with Cody Cook
DESCRIPTION: This week, Cody Cook rejoin us to talk about the incarnation of Christ. We look at the story of the Sons of God and the Nephilim and how the birth of Christ directly attacked this perverse paradigm. We also delve into the redemptive nature of the incarnation itself.
